Palmer's Tummy Butter for Stretch Marks (125 g)

A rich concentrated formula that can be applied liberally over the tummy as an intensive treatment. Contains soothing lavender oil which makes it ideal for evening application to promote relaxation and sleep. For best results use in conjunction with Palmer?s Massage Lotion for Stretch Marks for all-over body and Palmer?s Massage Cream for Stretch Marks for targeted areas. Our new advanced formula contains Bio C-Elaste
column13:
